<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>@ViewData["Title"]</title>
    <style>
        body {
            font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
            background-color: #f5f5f5;
            color: #333;
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
        }

        .container {
            max-width: 800px;
            margin: 0 auto;
            padding: 20px;
        }

        h1 {
            color: #009688;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
            text-align: center;
        }

        section {
            background-color: #fff;
            border-radius: 10px;
            padding: 20px;
            margin-bottom: 30px;
        }

        h2 {
            color: #009688;
            margin-bottom: 15px;
        }

        p {
            line-height: 1.6;
        }

        .footer {
            text-align: center;
            margin-top: 30px;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>

    <div class="container">
        <h1>@ViewData["Title"]</h1>

        <section>
            <h2>Introduction</h2>
            <p>Welcome to KhumaloCraft Emporium's Privacy Policy. This page outlines our policies regarding the collection, use, and disclosure of personal information when you use our website.</p>
        </section>

        <section>
            <h2>Information Collection and Use</h2>
            <p>We collect various types of information for different purposes to provide and improve our service to you.</p>

            <h3>Types of Data Collected</h3>
            <p>Personal Data: While using our service, we may ask you to provide us with certain personally identifiable information that can be used to contact or identify you. This may include your name, email address, postal address, and phone number.</p>
            <p>Usage Data: We may collect information on how you use the Service and the duration of such usage.</p>
        </section>
    </div>

    <div class="footer">
        <p>© 2024 - KhumaloCraft Emporium - <a href="#">Privacy</a></p>
    </div>

</body>
</html>
